		</a>
		<h1 class="title">好妹妹乐队是怎样众筹一场北京工体演唱会的？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3926/small/3926.jpg?1421980719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">费丽婷 刘平安</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-12 13:30:35 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
		<img src="/system/articles/longshows/13362/medium/13362.jpg?1439347761" alt="" />
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13362" data-title="《好妹妹乐队是怎样众筹一场北京工体演唱会的？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13362/medium/13362.jpg?1439347681" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13362" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
